{"tid":2432639,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[估國家] 立法規範 聾人應用手語“唱”國歌","createTime":"2021-03-04T12:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T12:54:25.000Z","uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e325ed686abca64cc11890c4e01787fb668623","tid":2432639,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"《〈中華人民共和國國歌〉國家通用手語方案》首次以聽力殘疾人手語使用者為主體，規範應用國家通用手語&ldquo;唱&rdquo;國歌，讓聽力殘疾人切實體會國歌的真實內涵，從而和全國人民一同領略國歌激發民族愛國情感、催人奮進的巨大作用。該規範的實施切實解決了多年來聽力殘疾人手語使用者在奏唱國歌場合，規範、統一、嚴肅使用手語表達國歌的願望，將使聽力殘疾人全面、準確感受國歌表現的民族精神，呼喚內心深處愛國主義情懷，促進我國殘疾人文化、教育事業的繁榮發展。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2021-03/01/content_5589446.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fxinwen%2F2021-03%2F01%2Fcontent_5589446.htm&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=2f5298a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2021-03/01/content_5589446.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?ref=search&amp;v=1639463329594277&amp;external_log_id=9314ad7b-7114-47a4-98ad-9a2085732b8e&amp;q=%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fref%3Dsearch%26v%3D1639463329594277%26external_log_id%3D9314ad7b-7114-47a4-98ad-9a2085732b8e%26q%3D%25E5%259B%25BD%25E6%25AD%258C%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AF%25AD%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyvxvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=d60809cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?ref=search&amp;v=1639463329594277&amp;external_log_id=9314ad7b-7114-47a4-98ad-9a2085732b8e&amp;q=%E5%9B%BD%E6%AD%8C%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E8%AF%AD%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"6ec74b3088f8e2adc0bd01b140dee11d25bde06c","tid":2432639,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p